                        </ol>
                    </nav>
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-white mb-4">Billing & Invoicing</h1>
                    <p class="lead text-white-50 mb-4">Time tracking, invoicing, and payment processing made simple. Get paid faster with professional invoices and online payments.</p>
                    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                        <i class="fas fa-rocket me-2"></i>Get Started Free
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-file-invoice-dollar fa-10x text-white-50"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Complete Legal Billing Solution</h2>

                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-stopwatch text-primary me-2"></i>Time Tracking</h4>
                            <p>Track billable time effortlessly with timers, manual entry, and batch time entry. Capture every billable minute.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>One-click timer start/stop</li>
                                <li>Batch time entry for multiple matters</li>
                                <li>Activity codes and descriptions</li>
                                <li>Non-billable time tracking</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-file-invoice text-primary me-2"></i>Professional Invoices</h4>
                            <p>Generate professional invoices in seconds. Customizable templates, detailed time entries, and expense tracking.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Customizable invoice templates</li>
                                <li>Automatic time entry import</li>
                                <li>Expense and disbursement tracking</li>
                                <li>PDF and email delivery</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-credit-card text-primary me-2"></i>Online Payments</h4>
                            <p>Accept credit card and ACH payments online. Clients can pay directly from their invoice with a secure payment link.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Credit card and ACH acceptance</li>
                                <li>Secure payment links</li>
                                <li>Automatic payment recording</li>
                                <li>Payment plans and recurring billing</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-chart-bar text-primary me-2"></i>Financial Reports</h4>
                            <p>Understand your firm's financial health with detailed reports. Revenue, collections, aging, and productivity at your fingertips.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Revenue and collection reports</li>
                                <li>Accounts receivable aging</li>
                                <li>Attorney productivity reports</li>
                                <li>Matter profitability analysis</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
